806
00:43:49,023 --> 00:43:49,804
Te saluto, Mara.

807
00:43:49,884 --> 00:43:50,384
Ragazzi!

808
00:43:54,690 --> 00:44:02,813
Sientate Paolo, scusami.

809
00:44:02,833 --> 00:44:05,655
